          vdVWLemma245CenteredEmpiricalSupremum P indexClass classFun
            (n + 1) sequence)
        ℱ (vdVWInfiniteProductMeasure P)) :
    ∀ᵐ sequence ∂(vdVWInfiniteProductMeasure P),
      ∃ limit : ℝ,
